# How to install NodeJS on Amazon Linux Workspace

### Configure Yum repo

```
sudo yum install -y gcc-c++ make 
curl -sL https://rpm.nodesource.com/setup_14.x | sudo -E bash - 
```

### Install 

```
sudo yum install -y nodejs 
```
### Check Version

```
node -v
```
